name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jinx: Aquatic Adventure in a Live Theme

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dive into Jinx’s aquatic adventures with vibrant water-themed visuals and handy shortcuts.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the chaotic and thrilling world of Jinx with this dynamic theme featuring sleek design and quick shortcuts.
Dynamic Live Wallpaper: Experience the vibrant and explosive energy of Jinx with dynamic visuals inspired by her iconic character.
Minimalist Design: A clean and edgy interface that reflects Jinx’s rebellious personality.
Clock and Date: Keep track of time and date at a glance while immersed in Jinx’s world.
Quick Access Shortcuts: Navigate instantly to your favorite websites with ease.
Google Search Bar: Perform fast and efficient searches with the engine selected by the user.
More Extension: Add exciting features to enhance your browsing experience with Jinx’s unique flair.
